{"tid":471573,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[game]跳幾下有錢收你會點揀?","createTime":"2017-11-17T11:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T17:07:00.000Z","uid":107157,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"eda74fcbfcc1155f5318bfba8a95346f1867de00","tid":471573,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T11:35:06.000Z","msg":"呢個遊戲係只要參加者係特定既高度跳落黎，就會有特定既獎金送比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下係幾條遊戲規則:<br />\n<br />\n1. 參加者需要跳總共30米既高度<br />\n2. 跳既高度可以自行分配<br />\n3. 玩家需要背向跳下<br />\n4. 遊戲場地分為石礫堆，石春地同埋太平洋海面，每個場地只能跳1次<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/191539_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F191539_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ac33625a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/191542_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F191542_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b34cdbfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/191545_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F191545_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=46b92258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 以下為獎金金額(hkd)，x代表跳既高度(米）<br />\na. 跳石礫堆既獎金為7既x次方<br />\nb. 石春地為x! (1*2*3*.....x)<br />\nc. 太平洋海面為扣除x*500萬<br />\n<br />\n6. 獎金唔可以轉移比第3方<br />\n7. 遊戲結束後最多負債1萬元<br />\n<br />\n如果我遲下將佢變成真實game，大家會點玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bedcab68321ed4b58511caf004e1ff45773d3e9b","tid":471573,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T11:36:57.000Z","msg":"想參加既留tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253605d4a6b677bd9d059f745545658b987672ef","tid":471573,"uid":5737,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T11:42:32.000Z","msg":"跳完 一係變殘廢一係就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95888120ffb01d0fd8082350d5117aa9c275ac69","tid":471573,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T11:43:05.000Z","msg":"比較想知 太平洋點跳<br />\n你包機送我地去太平洋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69312c3490051dfeaab1cd96cf15db070dcff2e7","tid":471573,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T11:44:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比較想知 太平洋點跳<br />\n你包機送我地去太平洋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n包你來回遊輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d36fc1dd001d72868c1d5ea9beeb70df268bb41","tid":471573,"uid":76908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T11:52:34.000Z","msg":"如果係得呢幾條規則我參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過跳完太平洋係咪一定有人救返上水先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29aaccf4f6d670f5d2036f4de68bcfdbd2fcc6f0","tid":471573,"uid":1928,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T11:56:56.000Z","msg":"唔死<br />\n醫藥費都收唔返 <br />\n玩唔過"},{"pid":"56aa6f35a9bd015879e4a4cf9755b4bad09d1967","tid":471573,"uid":157669,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T12:01:05.000Z","msg":"有bugs 無話背隻唔準攝野"},{"pid":"77af7cad4d3f3ab2fb97c8774683f60c0b73ee79","tid":471573,"uid":3698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T12:02:06.000Z","msg":"有無取巧工具<br />\n垂直定有斜坡例如圖一<br />\n可唔可以list 埋每個場每米幾錢"},{"pid":"84e7c409fe6e39cd1558dc8498f160be32d6cf7d","tid":471573,"uid":58140,"lik